VI'm a contemporary artist and I show in art galleries and museums.
p4
aVI show a number of photographs and films,
p5
aVbut I also make television programs, books and some advertising,
p6
aVall with the same concept.
p7
aVAnd it's about our fixation with celebrity and celebrity culture,
p8
aVand the importance of the image:
p9
aVcelebrity is born of photography.
